        {
          "text": "Turbo Charger equipped vehicle",
          "refs": [
            {
              "id": "R000413",
              "label": "Turbo Charger equipped vehicle",
              "resolved": true
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "11. Intercooler removal (turbo charger equipped vehicles)",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000418",
          "label": "Intercooler removal (turbo charger equipped vehicles)",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "12. Air cleaner stay removal (for vehicles not equipped with turbo charger)"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582178_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove purge hose clamp (A). Remove the air cleaner stay (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "13. Intercooler stay removal (for vehicles equipped with turbo charger)"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582179_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove purge hose clamp (A). Remove the intercooler stay (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "14. Heater hose Stay removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582180_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove heater hose (A) from heater hose stay (B). Remove the heater hose stays."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "15. Transmission side control wire removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582181_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the snap pin (A) and pull out the control pin (B). Remove the control wire bracket (C) and separate the control wire (D) from the control lever (E). Inspect the bushings (F) at the control wire ends for detachment, wear, or other damage. If there is damage, check for Replace control wires.",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000553",
          "label": "Replace control wires.",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Do not bend control wires more than necessary."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "16. Engine wire harness removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582182_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Disconnect the coupler (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582183_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "3",
      "text": "Disconnect the coupler (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582184_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "5",
      "text": "Disconnect the coupler (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582185_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "7",
      "text": "Remove the harness cover (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "17. リレー ボックス ステイ 取外し"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582186_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Disconnect the coupler (A). Remove the relay box stay (B). Remove each harness clamp (C) on the relay box stay."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "18. Purge Control SOL.V. Removal",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000505",
          "label": "Purge Control SOL.V. Removal",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "19. Sub Hangar Stay Installation"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582187_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Install the sub hanger stay using the spacer (A) and bolt (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "20. Engine support hanger installation"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582188_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Temporarily assemble the engine support hanger (AAR-T1256-J00) and install it aligning it with the upper parts of the left and right dampers and the front bulkhead as shown in the figure."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "21. Upper transmission case mounting bolt removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582189_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "22. Transmission mount removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582190_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the transmission ground cable terminal (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "23. Left Front Wheel Sensor Coupler Disconnect"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582191_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Disconnect the coupler (A) and remove it from the clamp (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "24. Lift Up"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "25. Remove front wheels on both sides"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "With the front wheels in the straight ahead position, both sides Remove the front wheel.",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000659",
          "label": "Remove the front wheel.",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "26. Transmission Fluid Extraction"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582192_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the drain bolt (A) and drain the transmission fluid."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "27. Front under cover removal",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000850",
          "label": "Front under cover removal",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "28. Front splash guard removal",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000849",
          "label": "Front splash guard removal",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "29. Transmission Fluid Warmer Removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582193_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Disconnect transmission fluid warmer (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11676648_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "2",
      "text": "Remove the O-ring (B) from the transmission fluid warmer (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "30. Solenoid wire harness coupler, driven pulley oil pressure sensor coupler Disconnect"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582194_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Disconnect the coupler (A). Remove the harness clamp (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Cover the coupler with a rag, etc. and be very careful to prevent dust, oil, etc. from entering the coupler."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "31. Exhaust pipe/silencer removal",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000416",
          "label": "Exhaust pipe/silencer removal",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "32. Transfer removal (4WD vehicles)",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000599",
          "label": "Transfer removal (4WD vehicles)",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "33. Tie rod end disconnect",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000644",
          "label": "Tie rod end disconnect",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "34. Stabilizer linkage disconnection (for vehicles equipped with stabilizer)",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000666",
          "label": "Stabilizer linkage disconnection (for vehicles equipped with stabilizer)",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "35. Lower ball joint disconnect",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000665",
          "label": "Lower ball joint disconnect",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "36. Torque rod removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582195_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Place a plate on the transmission and support it with a transmission jack, and remove the torque rod (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Do not loosen the torque rod mounting bolt (B)."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "When removing the transmission jack, lower it gradually as the engine moves forward."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "37. Subframe removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "544_5.0_jpn_11582196_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Support the sub-frame (A) with the transmission jack (B) by placing a square timber or similar object against the sub-frame (A). Remove the sub-frame mounting bolt (C). Remove the underload path mounting bolt (D). Remove the sub-frame."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "38. Transfer Breather Tube Assy. removal (4WD models)"
