      "text": "Install relay box stays (A) and relay box (B). Connect the coupler (C). Attach each harness clamp (D) to the relay box stay."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Ensure that there is no rust, debris, oil, etc. in the coupler."
      ]
